{"tid":416223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"T.O.P舊愛爆：下體比唇膏細","createTime":"2017-09-27T15:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T06:53:30.000Z","uid":29627,"like":508,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6370b6ffd40a0f961284ac1448776464f9f466","tid":416223,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170927/large/1506495770_37bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170927%2Flarge%2F1506495770_37bc.jpg&h=61ea5357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國天團BIGBANG成員T.O.P今年2月入伍，早前被爆與女練習生兼舊愛韓瑞希喺寓所吸毒，事後T.O.P同韓瑞希嘅大麻案都先後判刑，當中韓瑞希就判咗3年有期徒刑，緩刑4年執行。<br />\n<br />\n而韓瑞希日前忽然玩網上直播，自爆將於明年1月出道，當中更借T.O.P來炒作。原來喺當日直播中，韓瑞希仲暗示T.O.P下體嘅尺寸，表示：「佢下面比MAC嘅唇膏仲細。」雖然佢冇指名道姓話T.O.P，但網民都估計佢所指嘅就係舊愛，而網民就留言鬧爆佢咁樣有性騷擾T.O.P之嫌。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f155ca200597a921269ff550370dfb2fd2a0f","tid":416223,"uid":31261,"like":362,"dislike":2,"score":360,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"佢細個咁肥 發育不良好正常"},{"pid":"3f8ba4c4b98a4270bde717acdad1b5a435c84508","tid":416223,"uid":35014,"like":329,"dislike":1,"score":328,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eab5bc273f930af52cb703227fd4ccb0bc009ac","tid":416223,"uid":15476,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有調查指韓狗條撚係亞洲最短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去一去汗蒸幕就知 放家鏡都爭d搵唔撚到"},{"pid":"f37429b871663b572d3418abada3487c7e2e1d08","tid":416223,"uid":15476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前有調查指韓狗條撚係亞洲最短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去一去汗蒸幕就知 放<span style=\"color: red;\">大</span>鏡都爭d搵唔撚到</blockquote>"},{"pid":"308f57f362